Such an exciting day today, as hubby and I went out to pick up our new car!!I just love that new car feeling...even if it doesn't last long with kids and dogs etc, but we will enjoy the newness while we can!! I wore some vintage 501s that I recently got at the @yesteryearvintageclothing warehouse sale...I already have quite a few pairs, but they are so comfy, and they take me back to my youth so it's quite addictive!! This time I wore them with a thrifted Topshop bomber jacket and my new Adidas Superstars...one of my Mothers day presents...see @styledbysally ...flats...haha!!
